'''Scott Capurro''' (born [[December 10]], [[1960s#1962|1962]]) is a stand-up comedian and an author, and was the voice actor for [[Fodesinbeed Annodue|Beed]], the green head of the [[Podracing|podrace]] announcer, in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] and the video game [[Star Wars: Episode I Racer|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'']].

Scott Capurro was selected for the voice role of the red announcer in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. The other head of the character would be played by [[Greg Proops]]. Proops and Capurro would play again his double character in the video-game [[Star Wars: Episode I Racer|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'']].

He talked about his role in ''Star Wars'' in the documentary ''[[Star Wars: Feel the Force]]''.

